{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_01WSwx4UA3SPu8f3tEn4XcSX","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01CiKhiB24v2QsT59j61ZMdo","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Strawberry Shortcake Story.generated.24.txt","content":"STRAWBERRY SHORTCAKE STORY\n\nThere's something magical about the arrival of strawberries each spring. In my grandmother's\nkitchen, she would save the first ripe berries for this classic dessert—a celebration of warmer\ndays and fresh cream. The recipe has been passed down through generations, and each time I prepare it,\nI'm transported back to her flour-dusted apron and practiced hands working the dough with care. This\nversion combines tradition with modern ease, while honoring the simplicity that makes it so beloved.\n\nIngredients for Shortcake:\n- 225g all-purpose flour\n- 60g granulated sugar\n- 7.5ml baking powder\n- 2.5ml salt\n- 115g cold butter, cubed\n- 120ml heavy cream (plus extra for topping)\n- 5ml vanilla extract\n\nIngredients for Topping:\n- 900g fresh strawberries, sliced\n- 45g sugar\n- 480ml heavy cream\n- 30g powdered sugar\n- 5ml vanilla extract\n\nInstructions:\n1. Preheat oven to 200°C. Combine flour, sugar, baking powder, and salt.\n2. Cut in cold butter until mixture resembles coarse crumbs.\n3. Stir in cream and vanilla until dough just comes together.\n4. Drop spoonfuls onto baking sheet and bake 12-15 minutes until golden.\n5. Toss strawberries with 45g sugar, let sit 15 minutes.\n6. Whip cream with powdered sugar and vanilla.\n7. Layer shortcake, berries, and cream. Serve immediately.\n\nServes: 8 | Prep: 15 min | Bake: 15 min\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":21183,"cache_read_input_tokens":84762,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":21183},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"aa929ee3-74d9-4b58-8829-9858a8ab6a20","uuid":"02389388-1d65-469b-9b2d-cd20cc784f74"}
